claim.claim-text:
An airfoil (104) for a gas turbine engine, comprising:
a first cooling hole (201), having a first cooling passage (202) arranged at a first angle relative to a chordwise axis (D);
a second cooling hole (211), having a second cooling passage (212) arranged at a second, different angle relative to said chordwise axis (D), wherein a radial projection of said first cooling passage (202) intersects a radial projection of said second cooling passage (212).
